# Frontend Full Schema & Forms Update Plan

Aligning the Admin Panel frontend with all backend schema changes:
- Product pricing model (product-specific rates)
- UK-structured addresses (`county` + `postcode`)
- `vatExempt` on Client
- Full Booking model (UK addresses, products, waiting time)
- Full Invoice module (from scratch — create, list, view, PDF popup)

---

