## 6. Views / Forms

### [MODIFY] [ClientForm.tsx](file:///D:/Words4Web/RKB/RKB%20Admin%20Panel/src/views/clients/ClientForm.tsx)
- Address tab: `county` (optional, label "County"), `postcode` (required)
- Legal tab: Add `vatExempt` Switch toggle (separate from `vatRegistered`)

### [MODIFY] [ProductForm.tsx](file:///D:/Words4Web/RKB/RKB%20Admin%20Panel/src/views/products/ProductForm.tsx)
- New section **Unit & Pricing**: `unitType` Select, `basePrice`, `baseCharge`, `hourlyRate`
- New section **Waiting Time**: `waitingTimeRate`, `waitingTimeUnit` Select
- New section **Extra Charges**: dynamic add/remove rows `[{label, amount}]`
- Toggles below the form: `vatApplicable`, `defaultWaitingTimeApplicable`

### [REBUILD] [BookingForm.tsx](file:///D:/Words4Web/RKB/RKB%20Admin%20Panel/src/views/bookings/BookingForm.tsx)
- Tabbed layout: **Details** | **Locations** | **Products** | **Driver**
- Tab 1 – Details: Client select, Service Type, Scheduled Date/Time, Job Details
- Tab 2 – Locations: Pickup Address (UK), Drop Address (UK)
- Tab 3 – Products: searchable product select + qty + rate override (baseCharge/hourlyRate)
- Tab 4 – Driver: Driver select + Vehicle select

### [REBUILD] [InvoiceList.tsx](file:///D:/Words4Web/RKB/RKB%20Admin%20Panel/src/views/invoices/InvoiceList.tsx)
- Fetch real data from API; use React Query
- Status badge colours: Draft/Sent/Paid/Overdue/Cancelled
- "View PDF" button on each row → opens `InvoicePDFModal`
- "Create Invoice" button linked to `InvoiceForm`

### [REBUILD] [InvoiceDetails.tsx](file:///D:/Words4Web/RKB/RKB%20Admin%20Panel/src/views/invoices/InvoiceDetails.tsx)
- Fetch real invoice by ID
- Full document layout: company logo placeholder, company block, client block, line items table, Tax Breakdown (Net / VAT / Incl. VAT), Total, payment terms footer
- Button bar: **Download PDF**, **Print**, **Send to Customer**

### [NEW] InvoiceForm.tsx (`src/views/invoices/InvoiceForm.tsx`)
- Select booking (Completed only) → auto-populates line items from booking products
- Editable line items (description, quantity, unit price, VAT %)
- Auto-computed: `exVat`, `vatAmount`, `lineTotal`, `subtotal`, `totalVat`, `totalAmount`
- Fields: `dueDate`, `notes`, `transactionType`, `paymentLink`

### [NEW] InvoicePDFModal.tsx (`src/views/invoices/InvoicePDFModal.tsx`)
- Popup/dialog showing a printable invoice preview
- Uses company logo placeholder image
- "Download PDF" button using `window.print()` scoped to modal content (or `html2canvas` + `jsPDF`)
- "Close" button

